---------------------------------------------------------

getStorify Offers Pro Plugin - WordPress
================================================

Features:
------------
* List offers of a user
* List stores of a user
* List items of an offer of a store


How to use this plugin?
-------------------------
1. Go to the Plugins section in the WordPress Admin Dashboard and upload this plugin.
   If you have access to the server then you can also upload the plugin file using FTP softwares.

2. Activate the plugin.

3. Go to Settings page in the WordPress Admin Dashboard and select getStorify Offers Pro Plugin.

4. Enter the credentials like User ID, App ID and App Token and click on Save button.

5. You can now use the shortcode in your WordPress Page to show the stores and offers.